{
  "texts": [
    "The similarities between images were analysed using histogram intersection and the Chi-squared statistics to determine the distance obtained from the histograms of the two PHoG descriptors.",
    "The experimental design required the use of two ear datasets: the IIT Delhi ear database and the University of Notre Dame database (Collections E).",
    "The images were taken on several days with different poses and lighting conditions.",
    "The obtained data demonstrated the effectiveness of the Chisquared approach for determining distance.",
    "Similarly, the reduced PHoG based on LDA surpassed the normal PHoG in terms of speed and accuracy."
  ]
}